@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_xnuzny(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = (0.64 + (0.78 - (v0 + 0.93 * v2 + 0.32)))
    v2 = 0.24
    v1 = 0.81
    v0 = tmp
    v0 = tmp
    v0 = wp.cos(wp.cos(wp.cos(v1 + 0.73)))
    data[tid] = v0
